summary: I felt like Breezehome was garbage for a Thane, so I changed it...
descriptionHtml:
I didnt feel like Breezehome was good enough considering I was Thane of the city, so I changed it around and made it feel worthy of the Dragonborn.

Things added:
Grindstone
Workbench
Enchanters bench
Animal Head Wall mounts
and more...

Things Removed:
All the worthless crap laying around like boxes, sacks, and cups that nobody uses?

As always install at your own risk, I always buy all the upgrades for the homes CUZ IM RICH, but I changed things around without regard to the upgrades so Im not sure whats changed.

I did this for me, and am giving it to you, hope you enjoy it!
author: dsthebest
